    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs required 3) is offset by the strength of the output comparison results (all QoIs within 2% of experimental means, E/uval < 1.0) and the direct correspondence of the validation scenario to the COU. The FEA ensemble cross-model agreement further supports confidence in the simulation framework. Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence. Decision: Accepted.",
